'''PAM Development'''，又称'''Power and Magic Development'''，是总部设在法国巴黎的一家游戏开发商。公司成立于1995年，在2006年被[[Take_Two_Interactive|Take Two Interactive]]收购。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.games.ign.com/objects/499/499403.html |title=IGN: PAM Development<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-11-07 |archive-date=2011-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713004736/http://uk.games.ign.com/objects/499/499403.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.games.ign.com/articles/816/816338p1.html |title=IGN: 2K Games & 2K Sports Reveal GC Lineup<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-11-07 |archive-date=2011-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713004750/http://uk.games.ign.com/articles/816/816338p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/press-releases/31343/2K-Sports-Announces-Top-Spin-Tennis-for-Nintendos-Wiitrade |title=Top Spin Tennis - Press Releases - www.mcvuk.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2015-11-07 |archive-date=2007-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071010220842/http://www.mcvuk.com/press-releases/31343/2K-Sports-Announces-Top-Spin-Tennis-for-Nintendos-Wiitrade |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2008年6月，在发布《Top Spin 3》后不久，该工作室被[[2K_Games|2K Games]]关闭。

